THE PI WILL PRODUCE THE EXTENDED SEAFLUX DATASET, WITH THE MODIFICATIONS TO THE RETRIEVAL ALGORITHM AS OUTLINED IN THE PROPOSAL, SUCH THAT IT COVERS THE TIME PERIOD OF MID 1987 THROUGH AT LEAST 2009, AND THROUGH 2011 AS THE MORE RECENT ISCCP DATA BECOMES AVAILABLE. THE PI WILL ALSO DELIVER THE DEBIASED DATA SET.
